title: Wild Orchids (1929)
description:
Wild Orchids (1929) for the Coursera's Marriage and the Movies course.

This is the best quality video I could find, so I'm posting it here to be accesible to other students.

It isn't the best solution, there is Russian dubbing over it, but since it's silent movie it shouldn't be too much of a distress. Intertitles are there, in English of course.

Quality of the video isn't very good, but it is watchable, and it is only in case no better quality video appears this one I'm uploading this one.
